<script id="page1" type="text/xml"><?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"><text><body><p><pb facs="28b7a9e0-42fa-4d03-9681-2948e77f8c72"/><div><p>[The congés begins in the fourth column, 10 lines down]

explicit li sieges dataines li quitt
&amp; ci pres desdit jehan bodel
Pities &amp; ma matere puise
